text: Henry Nolan Mettetal (November 19, 1945 â€“ December 28, 2020) was an American politician. He was a member of the Republican party. Mettetal was member of the Mississippi House of Representatives from 2012 to 2020. He also was a member of the Mississippi Senate from 1996 to 2012. Mettetal was born in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. Mettetal died of COVID-19 on December 28, 2020 at a hospital in Oxford, Mississippi at age 75. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:2020 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Mississippi Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from Baton Rouge, Louisiana Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in the United States
